name: CellStar GB (v1.0)
description:
Play as a "cell" guy in this simple GameBoy game and get the stars while your time is ticking!!!

CONTROLS: MOVE USING THE D-PAD and START IS "NEXT".

YES, THIS IS REAL GAMEBOY SOFTWARE. YOU NEED AN EMULATOR/EVERDRIVE TO PLAY THIS ON. (Here's a list of them: https://www.emulator-zone.com/doc.php/gameboy/)

Questions? Ask in the comments!
